def continuous {X Y : Type} [topological_space X] [topological_space Y] (f : X → Y) : Prop :=
  ∀ V : set Y, is_open V → is_open (f ⁻¹' V)

def continuous {X Y : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] [TopologicalSpace Y] (f : X → Y) :=
  ∀ V : Set Y, IsOpen V → IsOpen (f ⁻¹' V)

def isContinuous {X Y : Type} [tX : TopologicalSpace X] [tY : TopologicalSpace Y] (f : X → Y) : Prop :=
  ∀ (V : Set Y), IsOpen V → IsOpen (f ⁻¹' V)

definition is_continuous {X Y : Type} [τ_X : TopologicalSpace X] [τ_Y : TopologicalSpace Y] (f : X → Y) : Prop :=
  ∀ V ∈ τ_Y.openSets, f ⁻¹' V ∈ τ_X.openSets

def is_continuous {X Y : Type} [τ_X : TopologicalSpace X] [τ_Y : TopologicalSpace Y] (f : X → Y) : Prop :=
  ∀ (V : Set Y), IsOpen V → IsOpen (f ⁻¹' V)

definition continuous {X : Type u_1} {Y : Type u_2} [τ_X : TopologicalSpace X] [τ_Y : TopologicalSpace Y] (f : X → Y) : Prop :=
  ∀ V ∈ τ_Y.IsOpen, τ_X.IsOpen (f ⁻¹' V)

def continuous {X Y : Type} [topological_space X] [topological_space Y] (f : X → Y) :=
∀ V : set Y, is_open V → is_open (f ⁻¹' V)

def Continuous {X Y : Type*} [tX : TopologicalSpace X] [tY : TopologicalSpace Y] (f : X → Y) : Prop :=
  ∀ V ∈ tY, f ⁻¹' V ∈ tX

def continuous {X Y : Type} [τ_X : TopologicalSpace X] [τ_Y : TopologicalSpace Y] (f : X → Y) : Prop :=
  ∀ V ∈ τ_Y, f ⁻¹' V ∈ τ_X

def continuous {X Y : Type} [tX : TopologicalSpace X] [tY : TopologicalSpace Y] (f : X → Y) : Prop :=
  ∀ V ∈ tY.is_open, f ⁻¹' V ∈ tX.is_open
